{"tid":2491750,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"荃西邊緣映日灣，重售成交1838萬，呎價23k ！","createTime":"2021-04-16T13:56:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T02:06:06.000Z","uid":388012,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"31c17ae396a9eea616f5f4a0e28b0d9c65cff626","tid":2491750,"uid":388012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T13:56:26.000Z","msg":"1838萬買荃灣映日灣撻訂戶 較2019年賣貴逾228萬<br />\n<br />\n億京荃灣已入伙新盤映日灣日前重推撻訂單位招標發售，今日首日招標截標，最終映日灣撻訂單位成功重售，價錢賣貴228.4萬元。<br />\n<br />\n映日灣成交紀錄冊顯示，1座18樓D室單位實用面積803平方呎，成交價錢為1838萬元，呎價22,889元。該單位原於2019年8月以1609.6萬元成交，已於今年1月8日終止買賣合約，今次重新售出賣貴228.4萬元或14.2%。<br />\n<br />\n是次售出單位每月管理費3344元，折合每呎管理費約4.16元，另地稅為2182.5元。順帶一提映日灣商場PLAZA 88陸續有店舖獲承租及開業。<br />\n<br />\n=======================<br />\n柏傲灣一房重售千二萬<br />\n映日灣都唔差"},{"pid":"fc003122a9fba51841cb3bc6f0dcb3afed1ed58c","tid":2491750,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:04:25.000Z","msg":"映日灣2房幾錢"},{"pid":"d821652b18d32d9c3db9ddcf7db262ad7420e7e8","tid":2491750,"uid":388012,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fc003122a9fba51841cb3bc6f0dcb3afed1ed58c","tid":2491750,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:04:25.000Z","msg":"映日灣2房幾錢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:12:05.000Z","msg":"未過SSD"},{"pid":"01e5e44159642ee71d4b47b0a83526ab3fb8a23e","tid":2491750,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d821652b18d32d9c3db9ddcf7db262ad7420e7e8","tid":2491750,"uid":388012,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fc003122a9fba51841cb3bc6f0dcb3afed1ed58c","tid":2491750,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:04:25.000Z","msg":"映日灣2房幾錢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:12:05.000Z","msg":"未過SSD"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:14:33.000Z","msg":"當年買係咪8-9球"},{"pid":"1d024cd5648bcd51ba99fa8a1b5d6471103baa10","tid":2491750,"uid":388012,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"01e5e44159642ee7